  <summary date="2023-05-23T13:59:12Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Prohibiting IRS Financial Surveillance Act 

This bill prohibits the Department of the Treasury from requiring a financial institution to report on an account's balance, transactions, transfers, or similar information. This prohibition does not apply to laws or regulations in effect on the date of enactment.</summary>
